import React from 'react'
import { Dropdown, Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const options = [
  { key: 1, text: 'Choice 1' },
  { key: 2, text: 'Choice 2' },
  { key: 3, text: 'Choice 3' },
]

const SearchFilter = () => (
  <Menu compact>
    <Dropdown text='Dropdown' options={options} simple item />
  </Menu>
)

export default SearchFilter
